---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Start — Your first brand.md, today. | Encoded" description="Copy the prompt. Paste it into any AI. Get a complete BCP tree for your brand in 15 minutes. Publish it at your domain.">
<style is:global>
/* ================================================================
   DESIGN SYSTEM — shared with index.html
   ================================================================ */
:root {
  --paper:    #FAFAF6;
  --paper-2:  #F0EDE6;
  --ink:      #0F0F0D;
  --ink-2:    #2B2923;
  --ink-3:    #6B6560;
  --ink-4:    #928C85;
  --rule:     #0F0F0D;
  --rule-soft: rgba(15,15,13,.10);
  --accent:   #B33D2A;
  --accent-warm: #D48845;
  --moss:     #3B4A2A;
  --sky:      #2A3B5C;

  --sans:  'Space Grotesk', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
  --serif: 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif;
  --mono:  'IBM Plex Mono', 'SF Mono', Menlo, monospace;

  --container: 1280px;
  --gutter: clamp(20px, 4vw, 56px);
  --idx-col: 160px;
}

/* ================================================================
   RESET + BASE
   ================================================================ */
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }
html, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body {
  background: var(--paper);
  color: var(--ink);
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.55;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

body::before {
  content: "";
  position: fixed; inset: 0;
  pointer-events: none; z-index: 1;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% -5%, rgba(179,61,42,.04), transparent 50%);
}

a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
::selection { background: var(--accent); color: var(--paper); }

/* ================================================================
   LAYOUT
   ================================================================ */
.wrap {
  max-width: var(--container);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 var(--gutter);
  position: relative;
  z-index: 5;
}

/* ================================================================
   BUTTONS
   ================================================================ */
.btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 13px 20px;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 13px;
  letter-spacing: .04em;
  border: 1px solid var(--ink);
  background: var(--ink);
  color: var(--paper);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background .2s ease, border-color .2s ease, transform .2s ease;
}
.btn:hover {
  background: var(--accent);
  border-color: var(--accent);
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}
.btn .arrow { transition: transform .2s ease; }
.btn:hover .arrow { transform: translateX(3px); }
.btn.ghost {
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--ink);
}
.btn.ghost:hover {
  background: var(--ink);
  color: var(--paper);
  border-color: var(--ink);
}
.btn.accent-bg {
  background: var(--accent);
  border-color: var(--accent);
}
.btn.accent-bg:hover {
  background: var(--ink);
  border-color: var(--ink);
}
.btn.big {
  padding: 18px 28px;
  font-size: 14px;
}

/* ================================================================
   NAV
   ================================================================ */
.nav {
  position: sticky; top: 0;
  z-index: 50;
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px) saturate(1.15);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px) saturate(1.15);
  background: rgba(250,250,246,.82);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule-soft);
}
.nav .wrap {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  height: 64px;
}
.nav-brand {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  gap: 8px;
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-weight: 400;
  font-size: 22px;
  letter-spacing: -.01em;
}
.nav-brand .bullet {
  width: 7px; height: 7px;
  background: var(--accent);
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: inline-block;
  translate: 0 -3px;
}
.nav-brand small {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: .16em;
  color: var(--ink-3);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-weight: 400;
  margin-left: 8px;
}
.nav-links { display: flex; gap: 28px; align-items: center; }
.nav-link {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 12px;
  letter-spacing: .04em;
  color: var(--ink-2);
  position: relative;
}
.nav-link::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  left: 0; right: 100%;
  bottom: -4px; height: 1px;
  background: var(--ink);
  transition: right .3s ease;
}
.nav-link:hover::after { right: 0; }
.nav-link.active { color: var(--accent); }
.nav-cta {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 12px;
  padding: 8px 14px;
  border: 1px solid var(--ink);
  transition: background .2s ease, color .2s ease;
}
.nav-cta:hover {
  background: var(--ink);
  color: var(--paper);
}
@media (max-width: 820px) { .nav-links { display: none; } }

/* ================================================================
   PAGE HERO
   ================================================================ */
.page-hero {
  padding: clamp(48px, 8vh, 88px) 0 clamp(24px, 3vh, 40px);
}
.page-hero .meta {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: .12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink-3);
  padding-bottom: 20px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  gap: 20px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.page-hero h1 {
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-weight: 500;
  font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 108px);
  line-height: .9;
  letter-spacing: -.04em;
  margin: 48px 0 0;
  max-width: 16ch;
}
.page-hero h1 em {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--accent);
  font-weight: 400;
}
.page-hero .lede {
  margin-top: 28px;
  max-width: 60ch;
  font-size: clamp(16px, 1.3vw, 19px);
  color: var(--ink-2);
  line-height: 1.55;
}
.page-hero .lede b { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }

/* ================================================================
   STEP SECTIONS
   ================================================================ */
.step-section {
  padding: clamp(56px, 8vh, 96px) 0;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
}
.step-head {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: var(--idx-col) minmax(0, 1fr);
  gap: 32px;
  align-items: baseline;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}
@media (max-width: 700px) { .step-head { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 14px; } }
.step-head .idx {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: .16em;
  color: var(--accent);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-weight: 500;
}
.step-head h2 {
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-weight: 500;
  font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 60px);
  letter-spacing: -.03em;
  margin: 0;
  line-height: .98;
}
.step-head h2 em {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--accent);
  font-weight: 400;
}
.step-head .sub {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: .1em;
  color: var(--ink-3);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-top: 8px;
}

.step-body {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: var(--idx-col) minmax(0, 1fr);
  gap: 32px;
}
@media (max-width: 700px) { .step-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 14px; } }
.step-body p {
  color: var(--ink-2);
  font-size: 17px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  max-width: 64ch;
  margin: 0 0 16px;
}
.step-body p b { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }
.step-body code {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: .9em;
  background: var(--paper-2);
  padding: 1px 6px;
  border: 1px solid var(--rule-soft);
}
.step-body ol, .step-body ul {
  color: var(--ink-2);
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  padding-left: 20px;
  margin: 16px 0;
}
.step-body li { margin-bottom: 8px; }

/* ================================================================
   PROMPT BLOCK — hero imagery of this page
   ================================================================ */
.prompt-zone { margin-top: 36px; position: relative; }

.prompt-callout {
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  padding: 20px 24px;
  background: var(--paper-2);
  border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
  font-size: 15px;
  line-height: 1.55;
  color: var(--ink-2);
}
.prompt-callout b { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }
.prompt-callout.alt {
  border-left-color: var(--sky);
}

.prompt-block {
  background: var(--ink);
  color: #e6e0d3;
  overflow: hidden;
  position: relative;
  border: 1px solid var(--ink);
  box-shadow: 12px 12px 0 var(--accent);
}
.prompt-header {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 14px 20px;
  background: #000;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(250,250,246,.1);
}
.prompt-header .label {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: .14em;
  color: var(--accent-warm);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-weight: 500;
}
.prompt-header .copy-btn {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 12px;
  letter-spacing: .06em;
  color: var(--paper);
  background: var(--accent);
  border: 0;
  padding: 8px 16px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background .2s ease;
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}
.prompt-header .copy-btn:hover { background: var(--accent-warm); color: var(--ink); }
.prompt-header .copy-btn.copied { background: var(--moss); color: var(--paper); }

.prompt-body {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 12.5px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  padding: 24px;
  white-space: pre-wrap;
  max-height: 420px;
  overflow: hidden;
  position: relative;
  color: #e6e0d3;
  margin: 0;
}
.prompt-body::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 120px;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--ink) 90%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.prompt-body.expanded { max-height: none; }
.prompt-body.expanded::after { display: none; }

.expand-btn {
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  padding: 14px 20px;
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--accent-warm);
  border: 0;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(250,250,246,.1);
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 12px;
  letter-spacing: .08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background .2s ease;
}
.expand-btn:hover { background: rgba(179,61,42,.1); color: var(--paper); }

/* agent chooser strip */
.agents {
  margin-top: 24px;
  display: flex;
  gap: 14px;
  align-items: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--ink-3);
}
.agents .label {
  letter-spacing: .12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink-4);
  font-size: 11px;
}
.agents a {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  padding: 7px 12px;
  border: 1px solid var(--rule-soft);
  color: var(--ink-2);
  background: var(--paper);
  transition: border-color .2s ease, background .2s ease;
}
.agents a:hover { border-color: var(--ink); background: var(--paper-2); }

/* ================================================================
   PATH CARDS
   ================================================================ */
.paths {
  margin-top: 32px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 14px;
}
@media (max-width: 860px) { .paths { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

.path {
  padding: 28px 24px 26px;
  background: var(--paper);
  border: 1px solid var(--ink);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  min-height: 200px;
  transition: transform .25s ease, box-shadow .25s ease;
}
.path:hover {
  transform: translateY(-3px);
  box-shadow: 12px 12px 0 var(--ink);
}
.path .tag {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: .14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink-3);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.path h3 {
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-weight: 500;
  font-size: 22px;
  letter-spacing: -.01em;
  margin: 0 0 10px;
  line-height: 1.15;
}
.path h3 em {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--accent);
  font-weight: 400;
}
.path p {
  color: var(--ink-2);
  font-size: 14.5px;
  line-height: 1.55;
  margin: 0 0 16px;
  flex: 1;
}
.path .path-link {
  align-self: flex-start;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 12px;
  letter-spacing: .04em;
  color: var(--accent);
  text-decoration: underline;
  text-underline-offset: 4px;
  text-decoration-thickness: 1px;
  transition: color .2s ease;
}
.path .path-link:hover { color: var(--ink); }

/* ================================================================
   CODE BLOCK
   ================================================================ */
.code-block {
  margin: 18px 0;
  background: var(--ink);
  color: #e6e0d3;
  padding: 22px 24px;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 13px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  overflow-x: auto;
  white-space: pre;
  border: 1px solid var(--ink);
  box-shadow: 12px 12px 0 var(--ink);
}
.code-block .comment { color: var(--ink-4); font-style: italic; }

/* ================================================================
   CLOSING CTA
   ================================================================ */
.closing {
  margin-top: clamp(72px, 10vh, 120px);
  padding: clamp(100px, 14vh, 200px) 0;
  background: var(--ink);
  color: var(--paper);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.closing::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 8% 8%, rgba(179,61,42,.1), transparent 50%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 92% 92%, rgba(42,59,92,.12), transparent 50%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.closing .wrap { position: relative; z-index: 2; }
.closing h2 {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-weight: 400;
  font-size: clamp(32px, 4.5vw, 56px);
  letter-spacing: -.02em;
  line-height: 1.08;
  margin: 0;
  max-width: 22ch;
}
.closing h2 em {
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--accent-warm);
  font-weight: 400;
}
.closing p {
  margin-top: 20px;
  color: rgba(250,250,246,.7);
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  max-width: 56ch;
}
.closing .ctas {
  margin-top: 28px;
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.closing .btn.ghost {
  color: var(--paper);
  border-color: var(--paper);
}
.closing .btn.ghost:hover {
  background: var(--paper);
  color: var(--ink);
}

/* ================================================================
   FOOTER
   ================================================================ */
footer {
  background: var(--ink);
  color: rgba(250,250,246,.7);
  padding: 72px 0 28px;
}
.foot-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 2.5fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
  gap: clamp(24px, 4vw, 56px);
}
@media (max-width: 820px) { .foot-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
@media (max-width: 520px) { .foot-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

.foot-brand {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(56px, 12vw, 180px);
  line-height: .88;
  letter-spacing: -.04em;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--paper);
}
.foot-brand .fdot {
  display: inline-block;
  width: .14em; height: .14em;
  background: var(--accent);
  border-radius: 50%;
  translate: 0 -.08em;
}
.foot-sub {
  margin-top: 18px;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 12px;
  color: rgba(250,250,246,.5);
  letter-spacing: .1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.foot-col h5 {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: .16em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent-warm);
  font-weight: 500;
  margin: 0 0 16px;
}
.foot-col ul {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0; margin: 0;
  display: grid; gap: 10px;
  font-size: 14px;
}
.foot-col a { transition: color .2s ease; }
.foot-col a:hover { color: var(--accent-warm); }
.foot-bottom {
  margin-top: 72px;
  padding-top: 20px;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(250,250,246,.1);
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 12px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: .1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink-4);
}

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  *, *::before, *::after { animation: none !important; transition: none !important; }
}
</style>

<header class="page-hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="meta">
      <span>Encoded · Start</span>
      <span>Free · Any AI · ~15 min</span>
    </div>
    <h1>Your first brand.md. <em>Today.</em></h1>
    <p class="lede">
      Copy the prompt below. Paste it into Claude, ChatGPT, Cowork, or whatever AI you already use. It will <b>interview you for about fifteen minutes</b>, then hand you back a complete set of BCP files ready to publish at your domain. <b>No signup. No account. Free forever.</b>
    </p>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- STEP 01 — COPY THE PROMPT -->
<section class="step-section" id="copy-prompt">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="step-head">
      <div>
        <div class="idx">Step 01</div>
        <div class="sub">1 minute</div>
      </div>
      <h2>Copy the <em>prompt</em>.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="step-body">
      <div class="spacer"></div>
      <div>
        <p>This is a senior brand strategist, compressed into a single prompt. Paste it into any AI. It knows how to interview you, what to push back on, and exactly what files to produce.</p>

        <div class="prompt-zone">
          <div class="prompt-callout">
            <b>Not technical? Good.</b> You don't need to edit this. Copy it verbatim. Paste it into the AI you already use. Answer the questions in your own words.
          </div>

          <div class="prompt-callout alt">
            <span style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sky);display:block;margin-bottom:6px;font-weight:500">Which AI to use</span>
            Works well with <b>Claude</b> (any model), <b>ChatGPT</b> (GPT-4+), <b>Cowork</b>, and <b>Gemini 2.5 Pro</b>. Free-tier Gemini and weaker models sometimes ignore the one-question-at-a-time instruction and flood you with everything at once. If that happens, tell the AI "<i>stop — ask one question, wait for my reply</i>." If it still misbehaves, switch to a smarter model.
          </div>

          <div class="prompt-block">
            <div class="prompt-header">
              <span class="label">BCP Authoring Prompt · v0.1</span>
              <button class="copy-btn" id="copyBtn" onclick="copyPrompt()">
                <span id="copyLabel">Copy to clipboard</span>
              </button>
            </div>
            <pre class="prompt-body" id="promptBody"><span id="promptText">You are helping me author a Brand Context Protocol (BCP) for my brand. A BCP is a set of markdown files that describe my brand in a way AI agents can read — every agent in my marketing stack, every vendor platform, and every consumer-facing AI (ChatGPT, Claude, Perplexity, Gemini) that might talk about my brand. The spec lives at https://encodedbrands.com. I am adopting it.

Your job: interview me, then produce a complete BCP tree as seven markdown files I can publish at `mydomain.com/.well-known/brand.md` and `mydomain.com/.well-known/brand/*.md`.

## Interview rules — READ CAREFULLY

**ONE question at a time. Then STOP.** Do not write a second question. Do not preview. Do not summarize. After each question: STOP, wait for my reply, then ask the next one.

If you find yourself generating multiple questions in a single response, you are violating these rules. Stop after the first question mark.

## Part 0 — What have you got? (ASK THIS FIRST)

Before the interview starts, ask me: **"What have you got?"**

Do I have existing brand documents — brand guidelines, strategy decks, mission/vision statements, a pitch deck, tone-of-voice docs, an 'About' page? Anything in writing that describes the brand already?

Offer three ways to share: paste text, upload files, or link to public URLs (my homepage, about page, blog).

If I share materials: read them carefully, pre-fill answers to the 18 interview questions, and only ask me about the gaps. Don't re-interview me on things you already know.

If I say "I don't have anything," start the interview at Question 1.

[... followed by 18 interview questions across Identity, Voice, Values, Boundaries, Claims, and Representation — plus the seven file templates. Full prompt is ~1,500 words. Copy the whole thing into your AI of choice.]</span></pre>
            <button class="expand-btn" id="expandBtn" onclick="expandPrompt()">Show full prompt ↓</button>
          </div>

          <div class="agents">
            <span class="label">Works with:</span>
            <a href="https://claude.ai/new" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Claude →</a>
            <a href="https://chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ChatGPT →</a>
            <a href="https://gemini.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gemini →</a>
            <a href="https://www.perplexity.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Perplexity →</a>
            <span style="color:var(--ink-4)">· and any other chat-based AI</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STEP 02 — ANSWER THE QUESTIONS -->
<section class="step-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="step-head">
      <div>
        <div class="idx">Step 02</div>
        <div class="sub">15 minutes</div>
      </div>
      <h2>Answer the <em>interview</em>.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="step-body">
      <div class="spacer"></div>
      <div>
        <p>The AI will ask you eighteen questions across six parts. Answer them in your own words. <b>Be specific.</b> Vague inputs produce vague BCPs — and a vague BCP does nothing for your brand.</p>
        <p>You'll cover:</p>
        <ol>
          <li><b>Identity</b> — who you are, who you serve, how you're different from your competitors.</li>
